1
00:00:07,725 --> 00:00:11,711
笙ｪI found a faint light
in the fading dusk笙ｪ

2
00:00:11,712 --> 00:00:15,311
笙ｪAnd met your steady gaze笙ｪ

3
00:00:15,312 --> 00:00:24,132
笙ｪOne knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on笙ｪ

4
00:00:24,575 --> 00:00:27,061
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

5
00:00:27,062 --> 00:00:29,211
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

6
00:00:29,212 --> 00:00:32,699
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

7
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:40,324
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

8
00:00:40,325 --> 00:00:42,786
笙ｪWe made a promise long ago笙ｪ

9
00:00:42,787 --> 00:00:44,786
笙ｪFor all our days to come笙ｪ

10
00:00:44,787 --> 00:00:48,449
笙ｪYou are the fate I cannot outrun笙ｪ

11
00:00:48,450 --> 00:00:53,836
笙ｪHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?笙ｪ

12
00:00:53,837 --> 00:00:56,457
笙ｪHolding you close笙ｪ

13
00:00:56,637 --> 00:00:58,874
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

14
00:00:58,875 --> 00:00:59,619
=Echoes of Love=

15
00:00:59,620 --> 00:01:01,207
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

16
00:01:01,712 --> 00:01:03,645
=Episode 5=

17
00:01:04,820 --> 00:01:05,498
My apologies.

18
00:01:05,499 --> 00:01:06,980
Sorry for the interruption.

19
00:01:14,940 --> 00:01:16,595
How long are you going
to stay on top of me?

20
00:01:25,499 --> 00:01:26,939
Sorry.

21
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:33,429
Why are you looking at me like that?

22
00:01:33,660 --> 00:01:35,379
I only did it for your sake.

23
00:01:36,859 --> 00:01:39,099
Besides, I didn't
actually take advantage of you.

24
00:01:46,059 --> 00:01:47,780
For someone
so bent on self-preservation,

25
00:01:47,820 --> 00:01:49,739
I offered you a way out,
and you refused.

26
00:01:50,699 --> 00:01:52,299
That is rather unexpected.

27
00:01:53,750 --> 00:01:55,800
You could simply admit
you were worried about me.

28
00:01:57,660 --> 00:01:58,579
Official Gu,

29
00:01:58,662 --> 00:02:00,138
I am not your subordinate.

30
00:02:00,139 --> 00:02:01,620
I do not answer to you.

31
00:02:01,660 --> 00:02:03,659
Why can you investigate, but I cannot?

32
00:02:05,339 --> 00:02:06,459
Investigate?

33
00:02:07,499 --> 00:02:10,539
- Even at the cost of your life?
- Yes. I will investigate.

34
00:02:10,939 --> 00:02:12,699
They forced me into a dead end.

35
00:02:12,700 --> 00:02:14,419
Why should I sit and wait to die?

36
00:02:14,775 --> 00:02:17,780
If I fight with everything I have,
then so be it.

37
00:02:17,819 --> 00:02:18,659
In any case,

38
00:02:18,779 --> 00:02:20,939
I will be the one to stir this storm.

39
00:02:22,140 --> 00:02:24,020
Then think it through.

40
00:02:24,339 --> 00:02:25,699
If you choose to be my blade,

41
00:02:25,825 --> 00:02:28,180
you will face countless dangers.

42
00:02:28,619 --> 00:02:29,819
Do not regret it.

43
00:02:31,950 --> 00:02:33,338
Once the blade is drawn,

44
00:02:33,339 --> 00:02:34,740
there is no regret.

45
00:02:38,312 --> 00:02:40,192
That is the auction master
of the Shengtang Guild.

46
00:02:40,687 --> 00:02:42,207
At every grand festival and banquet,

47
00:02:42,539 --> 00:02:43,218
he appears

48
00:02:43,219 --> 00:02:45,157
to select the most talented performers,

49
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:49,139
and present them to high officials
and nobles for their choosing.

50
00:02:49,539 --> 00:02:50,899
Just now, to save his own skin,

51
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:52,058
he told the truth.

52
00:02:52,059 --> 00:02:53,340
He said the Shengtang Guild

53
00:02:53,420 --> 00:02:55,045
has a Beauty Portrait.

54
00:02:55,140 --> 00:02:57,099
It records everything.

55
00:02:58,499 --> 00:03:00,259
Looks like this Beauty Portrait

56
00:03:00,260 --> 00:03:02,979
is the key to the whole truth.

57
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:07,459
At this Flower Festival,

58
00:03:07,460 --> 00:03:09,000
Su Wanniang has already won the crown.

59
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,859
She will surely be chosen
by the Shengtang Guild.

60
00:03:10,860 --> 00:03:11,618
When that happens,

61
00:03:11,619 --> 00:03:13,419
I will go with her
as her makeup attendant.

62
00:03:13,499 --> 00:03:14,274
I will slip in.

63
00:03:14,275 --> 00:03:15,498
We will work from inside and out

64
00:03:15,499 --> 00:03:17,460
and get the Beauty Portrait.

65
00:03:35,412 --> 00:03:39,019
笙ｪEven if I drift
within a darkened whirl笙ｪ

66
00:03:39,900 --> 00:03:41,179
This is...

67
00:03:41,180 --> 00:03:42,939
My people are all over the Capital.

68
00:03:43,740 --> 00:03:45,180
No matter when or where,

69
00:03:45,619 --> 00:03:47,179
once the jade whistle sounds,

70
00:03:47,180 --> 00:03:48,740
I will appear.

71
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:50,659
That is unbelievable.

72
00:03:52,020 --> 00:03:53,020
By the way,

73
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:55,058
this one.

74
00:03:55,059 --> 00:03:56,218
It's not pretty,

75
00:03:56,219 --> 00:03:58,419
but I made it with my own hands.

76
00:03:58,420 --> 00:03:59,098
It is for you.

77
00:03:59,099 --> 00:04:00,811
To show I mean this partnership.

78
00:04:00,812 --> 00:04:04,074
笙ｪIn exchange, no one will ever know笙ｪ

79
00:04:04,075 --> 00:04:06,495
笙ｪI will wait笙ｪ

80
00:04:07,862 --> 00:04:10,536
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

81
00:04:10,537 --> 00:04:12,674
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

82
00:04:12,675 --> 00:04:16,295
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

83
00:04:17,380 --> 00:04:19,140
This is Falling Plum Makeup.

84
00:04:19,620 --> 00:04:21,820
You are annoying,

85
00:04:22,099 --> 00:04:23,859
but you do have skill.

86
00:04:24,099 --> 00:04:25,459
Be careful.

87
00:04:25,460 --> 00:04:27,580
Tonight is the courtesan queen ceremony.

88
00:04:27,820 --> 00:04:29,539
(How can it be tonight?)

89
00:04:29,659 --> 00:04:30,338
(Could it be)

90
00:04:30,339 --> 00:04:31,659
(the intelligence was wrong?)

91
00:04:32,419 --> 00:04:33,819
Be careful.

92
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:35,778
If I make a fool of myself
at the Shengtang Guild,

93
00:04:35,779 --> 00:04:37,179
just wait until I get back.

94
00:04:42,219 --> 00:04:44,098
Those who perform there

95
00:04:44,099 --> 00:04:46,440
are not only the most
dazzling performers in the Capital,

96
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:48,280
they also stand a chance
of marrying into a great family.

97
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:49,524
I, Su Wanniang,

98
00:04:49,525 --> 00:04:51,338
will be the next Ruyu.

99
00:04:51,339 --> 00:04:53,580
I will become a nobleman's wife.

100
00:04:53,700 --> 00:04:54,459
Fine.

101
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:55,538
Once I finish your makeup,

102
00:04:55,539 --> 00:04:56,499
I will tidy up

103
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:57,900
and go with you.

104
00:04:58,339 --> 00:05:00,298
You do not seriously
think you can go, do you?

105
00:05:00,299 --> 00:05:01,659
Do not dream.

106
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:04,059
An opportunity
like this is strictly confidential.

107
00:05:04,099 --> 00:05:05,298
Madam Du said

108
00:05:05,299 --> 00:05:06,499
not even maids are allowed,

109
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:07,739
let alone you.

110
00:05:08,859 --> 00:05:10,699
(They really are making
their move tonight.)

111
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:13,179
Hurry up. There is only fifteen minutes left.

112
00:05:20,099 --> 00:05:21,059
(This will not do.)

113
00:05:21,140 --> 00:05:23,140
(There is no time
to send word to Gu Chengye.)

114
00:05:23,700 --> 00:05:25,859
(If Su Wanniang leaves now,)

115
00:05:25,940 --> 00:05:27,340
(not only will the trail go cold,)

116
00:05:27,419 --> 00:05:28,859
(she may lose her life as well.)

117
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:46,059
(The plan has changed.)

118
00:05:46,060 --> 00:05:47,900
(Come to Huanyue House at once.)

119
00:05:48,580 --> 00:05:51,645
The courtesan queen makes her debut.

120
00:05:52,225 --> 00:05:57,282
(Jade Grove and Fair Trees)

121
00:06:16,025 --> 00:06:17,824
(Jade Grove and Fair Trees)

122
00:06:17,825 --> 00:06:20,557
(Huanyue House)

123
00:07:11,940 --> 00:07:13,940
(Ever since I came to this era,)

124
00:07:14,219 --> 00:07:16,580
(it feels as though fate
has been pushing me forward.)

125
00:07:17,979 --> 00:07:19,858
(This place is shrouded in deception,)

126
00:07:19,859 --> 00:07:21,179
(danger at every turn.)

127
00:07:25,162 --> 00:07:27,460
(If Gu Chengye had not
stepped in to protect me,)

128
00:07:27,659 --> 00:07:29,780
(I would have long since lost my life.)

129
00:07:30,620 --> 00:07:32,780
(But since I, Song Zhiyun, am here,)

130
00:07:33,060 --> 00:07:34,580
(Shengtang Guild,)

131
00:07:35,287 --> 00:07:37,642
(no matter what monstrous scheme
you hide behind,)

132
00:07:37,862 --> 00:07:39,804
(I will uncover it myself.)

133
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:42,520
(I will demand justice)

134
00:07:42,859 --> 00:07:44,460
(for those poor women.)

135
00:07:52,339 --> 00:07:54,379
That is phosphorescence.

136
00:07:54,380 --> 00:07:56,338
She is performing Dragon Fish Play.

137
00:07:56,339 --> 00:07:58,178
The lights and the dance
reflect one another.

138
00:07:58,179 --> 00:08:00,778
No wonder she is
the courtesan queen of Huanyue House.

139
00:08:00,779 --> 00:08:02,259
(Gu Chengye should have)

140
00:08:02,260 --> 00:08:04,179
(seen the note by now.)

141
00:08:04,859 --> 00:08:07,538
Ladies, your talents
are truly remarkable

142
00:08:07,539 --> 00:08:09,579
and exquisite beyond compare.

143
00:08:09,580 --> 00:08:12,299
Please come forward
one by one to receive your reward.

144
00:08:18,460 --> 00:08:20,858
To be adorned with a bloom
from the Shengtang Guild

145
00:08:20,859 --> 00:08:23,059
is the highest honor.

146
00:08:24,659 --> 00:08:26,260
The flower is beautiful.

147
00:08:41,860 --> 00:08:43,298
Honored guests,

148
00:08:43,299 --> 00:08:45,178
what we present tonight

149
00:08:45,179 --> 00:08:48,178
is a rare treasure
of the Flower Festival,

150
00:08:48,179 --> 00:08:49,458
radiant as a blossom,

151
00:08:49,459 --> 00:08:51,019
captivating in beauty.

152
00:08:51,220 --> 00:08:54,418
The first to ascend
the auction stage tonight

153
00:08:54,419 --> 00:08:56,219
is Red Begonia.

154
00:08:56,220 --> 00:08:57,379
Me?

155
00:08:57,900 --> 00:09:00,180
An auction? What is going on?

156
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:03,458
Opening bid, one hundred gold.

157
00:09:03,459 --> 00:09:04,820
One hundred fifty gold.

158
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:06,220
Three hundred gold.

159
00:09:06,779 --> 00:09:07,940
Five hundred gold.

160
00:09:07,980 --> 00:09:09,259
Five hundred gold.

161
00:09:09,579 --> 00:09:11,420
Any higher bids?

162
00:09:11,620 --> 00:09:13,340
Congratulations, honored guest.

163
00:09:13,659 --> 00:09:14,460
Take her.

164
00:09:19,459 --> 00:09:20,458
I'm not going with you.

165
00:09:20,459 --> 00:09:22,220
- Let me go.
- Hurry.

166
00:09:28,140 --> 00:09:28,899
Sir,

167
00:09:29,179 --> 00:09:30,818
my promotion

168
00:09:30,819 --> 00:09:32,180
depends on you.

169
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:33,859
Next.

170
00:09:33,860 --> 00:09:35,619
Start at two hundred gold.

171
00:09:36,380 --> 00:09:37,499
Five hundred gold.

172
00:09:39,179 --> 00:09:40,499
Five hundred gold.

173
00:09:42,659 --> 00:09:44,580
No. I'm not going.

174
00:09:47,537 --> 00:09:49,161
(So that is it.)

175
00:09:49,419 --> 00:09:52,460
(The Shengtang Guild
is using performers as bribes)

176
00:09:52,819 --> 00:09:54,180
(to form factions for private gain.)

177
00:09:58,699 --> 00:10:00,340
I don't want to go.

178
00:10:04,179 --> 00:10:05,458
The final one,

179
00:10:05,459 --> 00:10:06,979
the finest lady.

180
00:10:14,659 --> 00:10:16,058
Skin like polished jade,

181
00:10:16,059 --> 00:10:17,820
graceful as a willow in the breeze.

182
00:10:18,140 --> 00:10:20,899
This is the courtesan queen
of the Flower Festival,

183
00:10:21,220 --> 00:10:22,739
Pink Begonia,

184
00:10:22,860 --> 00:10:24,580
Su Wanniang.

185
00:10:25,380 --> 00:10:26,580
Opening bid,

186
00:10:26,659 --> 00:10:28,220
five hundred gold.

187
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:31,807
- Six hundred gold.
- Seven hundred gold.

188
00:10:35,179 --> 00:10:36,779
One thousand gold.

189
00:10:37,140 --> 00:10:38,739
One thousand five hundred gold.

190
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:41,139
One thousand five hundred gold.

191
00:10:41,539 --> 00:10:43,300
Any higher bids?

192
00:10:45,575 --> 00:10:47,365
Congratulations, honored guest.

193
00:10:54,980 --> 00:10:57,019
So close.

194
00:10:57,020 --> 00:10:59,219
Such a beauty has fallen into his hands.

195
00:10:59,220 --> 00:11:01,259
She may not even
leave a whole body behind.

196
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:03,259
I heard he even has a cellar,

197
00:11:03,260 --> 00:11:05,058
used to imprison women,

198
00:11:05,059 --> 00:11:07,580
with physicians kept on
standby in his residence.

199
00:11:11,539 --> 00:11:12,580
Sir,

200
00:11:12,740 --> 00:11:14,739
please accept this.

201
00:11:14,779 --> 00:11:17,460
As for my second brother,
who was sentenced to death,

202
00:11:18,179 --> 00:11:19,859
he will be released tomorrow.

203
00:11:20,425 --> 00:11:21,695
Thank you.

204
00:11:28,459 --> 00:11:30,019
Three thousand gold.
